{"tid":573311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豪宅管理員疑不滿冇得攞利是 攀上合和中心簷篷抗議","createTime":"2018-02-26T10:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T04:38:46.000Z","uid":1121,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc5631c2479b27889eddad242f53a68cac3da6b","tid":573311,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"【16：38更新】合和實業發言人回應稱，了解後得悉該員工不滿年初一上班時的工作安排<br />\n【15：03更新】新增影片<br />\n<br />\n灣仔皇后大道東183號合和中心，下午2時許，一名男子由二樓平台爬上大門口頂簷篷，披上寫有類似抗議字句的紙牌請願，救援人員接報到場，將男子勸服，將他帶返安全位置，警員正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，男子自稱為合和物業管理負責管理的樂景園屋苑職員，因不滿上司調職安排，令他在春節期間無法接觸客人，拿不到利是，而到場示威請願。<br />\n<br />\n合和實業發言人回應稱，經了解，涉事員工在由合和物業管理負責管理的樂景園屋苑工作，該員工報稱不滿年初一上班時的工作安排。據知他當日獲安排到停車場當值，但他曾稱希望到管理處當值，當時曾向上司反映不滿。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，該員工為合和物業管理的樂景園屋苑中擔任客戶服務助理，他於年初一後幾日一直請病假，今日他亦繼續請病假未有上班。<br />\n<br />\n對於有指事主不滿未能在管理處當值，以致未能向住客拜年取利是，發言人表示，一般而言，公司規定任何員工不可以主動向住客收取利是。"},{"pid":"832c2818604657bb638dd0abb72535faa5af5610","tid":573311,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180226&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57877107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180226%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57877107&d=NZ7uMZVkKH4XTvpQbMBpr8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=11e42ac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180226%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57877107&h=6896a7c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180226&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57877107</a>"},{"pid":"21b424c240e93bfc8bf4294f09865c4f01eb71f2","tid":573311,"uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180226/large/1519624442_475f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180226%2Flarge%2F1519624442_475f.jpg&h=05781dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男子爬上灣仔合和中心大門口頂簷篷，抗議請願。(張培生攝)"},{"pid":"3b6519d16297e0bfc9aad9ebdd82fafed1d75bd3","tid":573311,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b003b0874e55c1f98f9893b66c10a8e7f97a89","tid":573311,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:06:20.000Z","msg":"死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da8f50d6b0aff78433bfbc7b7bb2e9189cf5c98","tid":573311,"uid":24227,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:16:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">春節</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d18afed361ae4d27d2be231f582a1395b56729","tid":573311,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0fa80f9abfb21f9048d61d1b907ab192b6133a","tid":573311,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"本身諗住初一開始精神！點知去左守停車場"},{"pid":"d113cb1c08bf1edd109bac7296738a44e9705b78","tid":573311,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4f930314033327381d994d41f77e5527799eef","tid":573311,"uid":61675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:11:57.000Z","msg":"乜撚野春節啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b631437ba3cffe1e58d9759e83aecdce6daf3b","tid":573311,"uid":4942,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0